<section class="partners section">
  <div class="container partners__inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Built with</p>
    <h2>The partners behind the network.</h2>
    <p class="partners__lede">
      Rangeway is operated by a small team and built with partners across structure, energy,
      software, and driver experience.
      <a href="https://carbondc.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Carbon DC</a> anchors our
      off-grid sites,
      <a href="https://renuteq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ReNuTeq</a> builds every
      structure,
      <a href="https://ekoenergetyka.com/america/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ekoenergetyka</a>
      delivers the chargers, and
      <a href="https://chargemate.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ChargeMate</a> stands by
      every driver.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-link partners__cta" href="/partners">
      See all partners
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
        <polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18" />
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .partners__inner {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .partners__lede {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .partners__lede a {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(232, 146, 58, 0.32);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-standard),
      border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-standard);
  }

  .partners__lede a:hover {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-warm-deep);
  }

  .partners__cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
</style>
